[00:27.84]Whispers softly in the dark
[00:31.56]Give me grace to turn and run
[00:35.28]Before it takes my heart
[00:38.99]It’s better now to lose the lie
[00:42.71]Than lose the life You give
[00:46.43]You are worth it all
[00:50.15]You are worth it all
[00:53.86]If it pulls my heart from You
[00:57.58]I let it fall
[01:01.30]I let it fall
[01:05.02]No shadow stands, no idol calls
