[01:42.19]It’s better now to feel the fire
[01:45.91]Than live in silent chains
[01:49.63]You are worth it all
[01:53.34]You are worth it all
[01:57.06]If it pulls my heart from You
[02:00.78]I let it fall
[02:04.50]I let it fall
[02:08.21]No shadow stands, no idol calls
[02:11.93]Jesus, You are worth it all
